beer.beer_description: A special edition of our Three Sheets Pale Ale brewed in collaboration with our friends at the Marriott Hotel and Customs House Bar in Sydney. Using seasonal cascade hops from Virginia, it pays homage to Marriott Hotel's origins and the location of the very first hotel opened by Marriott in 1957.
